snippet.textDisplay: I love Lizzo's performance, but these girl shouldn't be on pointe. Less because they're thick but more because THEY DON'T KNOW WHAT THEY'RE DOING AND THAT'S DANGEROUS. I'm all for body diversity, but I'm not at all for risking the health and wellbeing of dancers for an aesthetic they clearly can't pull off. Any one of them could hurt themselves and not be able to dance anymore.
